    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>So powerful and brave. You will find your way in your new world, just as you have already many times in your lifetime. The curve balls we are thrown are difficult to handle, but you will manage this one with grace, humor, and dignity as you have in these written words. You are forging a new reality and we are here to support you all the way!</p>
