    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I have been reading your blog forever and have always appreciated your clear voice and honest perspective. One of the reasons I stopped blogging (besides a distinct lack of readership) was that I could no longer bear to share so many personal stories. You are brave and the community supporting you in your vulnerability is testament to all you&#8217;ve created. Also, I&#8217;m pretty sure that your third book is going to be really, really good.</p>
