    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Well, Molly, you are certainly a lady who has adventures, and this was a biggie in terms of voyages into the self.  It sounds like you and Brandon are handling this with genuine class &#8212; love of June, certainly the best of your joint creations &#8212; and love of the closeness that you have shared and will continue to share as dear friends.  All the best to the three of you in this new phase of your lives.  Life is altogether too short for us not to seek what we are born to be and embrace it. But we are not like snakes; we do not have to shed our old skin to emerge into the new, but can retain what is best of what we have been, and who we have been, while becoming what we are.</p>
