    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>You are so brave-both in writing this and in finding your truth in order to live your life the best you can. Thank you for writing about this and so many other difficult things. The chapter you wrote about your dad was the first one I turned to after my dad died and reading Delancey gave me so much to think about as I started my own marriage. I wish you love and light.</p>
