    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I have read this 3  times today.  It is stunning.  On top of all the wonderful, and wonderfully accurate things people are writing about you, I would like to add &#8211; not that you needed to hear it from a complete stranger &#8211; that Brandon is also, obviously, stunning, and so very brave, for walking through this with you when you let him in on it, and for continuing to be, as you put it, your very best friend.  That cannot have been easy.  I bet it&#8217;s still not easy &#8211; so my hat is off to him as well as you &#8211; you broke nothing.  you failed at nothing.  your marriage, was in every sense of the word, epically successful.  We should all be so lucky.  Love.</p>
