    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Molly, I&#8217;m a longtime reader and super fan (I brought A Homemade Life to a &#8220;favorite things&#8221; holiday party to share as my all-time favorite thing!), but this is the first time I&#8217;ve commented. I just lost my father to cancer last month, and I thought of your story many times. I&#8217;m a stranger to you, but you comforted me. I hope today YOU are comforted by strangers &#8211; and friends &#8211; who are proud of you for seeking and speaking your truth. You&#8217;re important to so many people you don&#8217;t even know. I wish you and your family all the best of life and love.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-59676' data-commentid="59676" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-59676" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to CJ" aria-label='Reply to CJ'>Reply</a>    </div>
  </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-59677" class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Amy Moore</cite></div>
      <a href="http://orangette.net/2016/11/november-30/#comment-59677"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2016-11-30T22:56:31-05:00">Wednesday, November 30, 2016 at 10:56 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Molly: I first read your post earlier today, and the experience has paced my entire mindset since I encountered your words. I love the reality of bravery requiring fear before it can even show up. Your story astounds my heart up with love and overflows my mind up with hope. I wish I could bottle up the love of your gorgeous fish family and blow it up all over every human in existence. I am astounded and stand with wonder and gratitude for your remarkable spirit. One day at a time.  -Amy in Nashville</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-59677' data-commentid="59677" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-59677" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Amy Moore" aria-label='Reply to Amy Moore'>Reply</a>    </div>
  </li><!-- #comment-## -->
