    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Emily</cite></div>
      <a href="http://orangette.net/2016/11/november-30/#comment-59678"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2016-11-30T22:57:37-05:00">Wednesday, November 30, 2016 at 10:57 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Oh Molly.  My heart aches for you and Brandon.  What a beautiful and scary and confusing experience this must be/have been.  I am so proud of and impressed by you both &#8211; your commitment and honesty and respect for each other and for your family is something so many married couples and families of all shapes and sizes strive for.   Love to you all.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-59678' data-commentid="59678" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-59678" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Emily" aria-label='Reply to Emily'>Reply</a>    </div>
