      <a href="http://orangette.net/2016/11/november-30/#comment-59680"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2016-11-30T22:59:55-05:00">Wednesday, November 30, 2016 at 10:59 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Thanks for being brave enough to live life the way it&#8217;s supposed to be lived! To keep on changing and growing and learning. So happy for you, and so so grateful for all the hope you carve into the world.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-59680' data-commentid="59680" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-59680" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Maddie Lee" aria-label='Reply to Maddie Lee'>Reply</a>    </div>
  </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-59682" class="comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Mary D</cite></div>
      <a href="http://orangette.net/2016/11/november-30/#comment-59682"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2016-11-30T23:20:13-05:00">Wednesday, November 30, 2016 at 11:20 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Molly, a wonderful therapist I heard at a nursing conference in Boston years ago said something I&#8217;ve never forgotten. She said, &#8220;if you want to be mentally healthy, you have to speak the truth&#8221;.  Your story isn&#8217;t about being brave or having courage ( although I know it has taken lots of both for you to write this blog  post) &#8211; it&#8217;s about speaking your truth. The very best gift you can give to yourself and those you love, especially Brandon and June. Please don&#8217;t stop writing. Now, more than ever, we need to be connected to people who speak their truth.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-59682' data-commentid="59682" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-59682" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Mary D" aria-label='Reply to Mary D'>Reply</a>    </div>
