    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I noticed you filed this under: AHH THE MYSTERIES OF THE UNIVERSE BIG THOUGHTS FAMILY FRIENDSHIP MARRIAGE SCARY STUFF WRITING.</p>
<p>It captures perfectly why I love your work. Wishing you the best.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-59683' data-commentid="59683" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-59683" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Mary" aria-label='Reply to Mary'>Reply</a>    </div>
  </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-59684" class="comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="http://nicoleciomek.com" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Nicole</a></cite></div>
      <a href="http://orangette.net/2016/11/november-30/#comment-59684"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2016-11-30T23:31:09-05:00">Wednesday, November 30, 2016 at 11:31 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>As someone who didn&#8217;t truly realize my bisexuality until I was in my mid-20s, I feel you. My husband has asked me directly if I find myself more interested in women than men. It comes from a place of wanting to make sure I&#8217;m fulfilled as a person and not just stuck in a routine.  I appreciate his sensitivity to my sexuality and it sounds like Brandon has been super understanding of you. That&#8217;s wonderful. This may not be what you imagined, but following who we are inevitably makes you happier. My husband and I have a non-monogamous marriage &amp; that was sort of at my instance. As we become more open with others about that, it&#8217;s been amazing how supportive/interested/curious people are. I&#8217;ve been pleased with the lack of judgment. I hope you find the same. Know that you will always have a supportive community at this blog. &lt;3 &lt;3 &lt;3 </p>
<p>As I tell my friends before parting ways,  &quot;You are perfect as you are.&quot;</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-59684' data-commentid="59684" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-59684" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Nicole" aria-label='Reply to Nicole'>Reply</a>    </div>
  </li><!-- #comment-## -->
