    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I honestly had started to panic, I thought maybe you had decided that the blog was too much in what was already a full life.  Then tonight I check again with trepidation hoping, hoping to see a new post and then I find this beautiful, honest open and amazing moment of woman sharing with us her most private life details in a way that moved me so much.  The love that of the people in your life is so clear, the fear and trepidation as your life moves in this new you, the concern and joy for your family. Thank you, for your honesty, for your willingness to share and mostly for writing.  ❤️</p>
