    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Molly,<br />
Your writing, intelligence, and sensibility have made their way into my heart and mind ever since I discovered your blog years back.   A gentle guide in how I even move about the kitchen and think about food.  And, now this.   Marriage, motherhood, self-hood, womanhood &#8211; we all struggle with the weight of it all and how incredibly complicated, confusing, wonderful, messy, and lonely it can all be.  Thank you for sharing your courage in such a way that makes us all feel held, whole, strong, and safe wherever we are in our journey.   I feel like I have changed just by reading your words.   I have so much admiration for you.</p>
