    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>This is the best thing you have ever written.<br />
You are incredibly brave.  Such vulnerability takes real strength,  be proud of that.  I have some experience of this and know how much it takes to speak your truth, so I genuinely admire you.  Also, please don&#8217;t be phased by all the people that immediately want to put you in a box (you are bi!  you are gay!  no you are a pink unicorn!).  In my experience many people can only be comfortable once you are properly *catagorised*.  Balls to that.  Nothing invalidates your marriage, you are a human that loved a man and now possibly a woman and who knows or cares if it&#8217;ll change again.  You are whatever you say you are.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-59706' data-commentid="59706" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-59706" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to aneke" aria-label='Reply to aneke'>Reply</a>    </div>
