      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Candace H.</cite></div>
      <a href="http://orangette.net/2016/11/november-30/#comment-59707"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2016-12-01T04:29:40-05:00">Thursday, December 1, 2016 at 4:29 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Hi Molly,</p>
<p>We have friends who, just last year, lived this exact scenario. They are now both infinitely happier and co-parenting well. She is very free and very different. I think because she has answered an inside voice telling her change had to be. </p>
<p>We love Delancey and love your story but all good real stories have surprises and easy, pretty parts and messy,confusing parts. After all anyway, it&#8217;s not a story, it&#8217;s your life. </p>
<p>Best wishes!</p>
