    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Molly,<br />
After having my own issues in my marriage recently, I found this particular writing so comforting.  As you have mentioned, very few of us are willing, able, or brave enough to talk about struggles in marriage and love because it sometimes feels like such a public admission of failure.  Not talking about it, however, does not mean so many of us go through these same struggles as we move through the world and our lives.  Thank you SO much for writing this.  I needed it more than I knew.  I have always admired your writing and ability to self-disclose so artfully; now more than ever.   Take care and only the best.</p>
    </div>

