    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Wow, you just left me breathless and inspired at the same time.  Your courage and strength are amazing and your writing is beautiful.  I wish you all the best in the new chapter of your life.  And of course I look forward to reading about your new adventures and thoughts about them.</p>
