    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Love is love is love is love is love.  I hope you are feeling the waves of it.  It is so lonely keeping such a big secret&#8230;so grateful you shared it with all of us in such a beautiful, brave, inspiring way.  I feel exhilarated and exhausted reading your words&#8211;can only imagine how you feel today!  I was so lucky to meet you in the summer of 2015 at book club&#8211;apparently just a couple months after this was all starting to go down&#8211;and we asked you questions about your book and your marriage (and that hot Axl Rose character), and you endured us and entertained us&#8211;I know you describe yourself as bumbling and flailing, but all I see is grace and beauty.</p>
