    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I wasn&#8217;t expecting this! I&#8217;m pretty sure I saw you, sitting on the steps of the French House the weekend I visited Stanford before attending. I thought then, as I think now, that I&#8217;d like to be like you someday, although I&#8217;m not a redhead and, as far as I know, not gay. I do of course have other challenges (more of the international love variety) and other fond memories of that same house. I&#8217;ve been reading your blog forever, and I&#8217;m both surprised and not surprised. I hope to have a chance to make it up to Delancey someday. I admire your courage and your blog in equal measure.</p>
