    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Oh Molly, I love you so much. Your honestly is beautiful and hard. Life is full of twists and turns that can be such a pain. You are navigating well, your compass is true. I wish we were real life friends so I could say. Come over with June, she can play with Delphine and Julien and we can have some tea and gingerbread and zone out or talk. Whatever. sometimes just sitting with someone is enough. Thank you for trusting us to hold you in our hearts.</p>
