    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Wow.  WOW!  I was really getting worried about you since posts have been less frequent lately.  This had to have been a tough post to write, let alone share with your online world.   Please know this:  you are loved by us, and we, your fan club, will always be there with you and for you.  Thank you for sharing.</p>
