    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Hugs. &#8220;It&#8217;s horrible&#8230; also better than I could have imagined&#8221;. And the ending paragraphs of Delancy&#8230;  wow.  I am glad you have this awesome relationship. This beautiful daughter. Your mom&#8230; (I am your mom in some ways, though my children are younger and in the current climate, it is not my position to out them, but I support them wholeheartedly). I wish you happiness as you navigate the horribleness. But. I think June will be just fine. Trust yourself and take the time you need. Let love and life happen.</p>
