    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Holy effing shit. I&#8217;d given up hope that I would hear the OG voice again, attributing the radio silence to election results/fleeing the country. &#8220;Brandon and I separated this summer&#8221; was, for me, the equivalent of a mic drop. Reading that for the first time, while lying next to my sleeping 2-year old at 1am last night, I read it and re-read it. Dang girl, I don&#8217;t know you but through your blog (which I have followed from the beginning) but count this reader as someone firmly in your crazy/mixed-up/awesome new family&#8217;s collective corner. Brandon and June are lucky to have you in their lives and vice versa.</p>
