    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Some days I look around me and I see so many of us late-coming-out lesbian or bi women it makes me smile (the UK gardening columnist Alys Fowler wrote a column recently about falling in love with a woman unexpectedly).</p>
<p>My heart sank when I read that you and Brandon are separated and rose again when I carried on reading. Congratulations for being brave, thank you for writing , and I wish you all the happiness in the world.</p>
    </div>

