    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>What a gift it is to live honestly, to allow yourself the chance to do what is right. I might be reading into this, but it seems Brandon has been able to be supportive during this. I am so grateful for both of you, that he could be so. June, she&#8217;s all set. Her parents love her and love each other, and they don&#8217;t need to live under the same roof to do that. She will know that there are multiple safe places in the world for her. Being brave, doing what is right despite how terrifying it might be or how much it might throw your life into temporary chaos, is what I wish for all women. They now have you as a model. Wishing you and yours all the love life can bring you.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-59878' data-commentid="59878" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-59878" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Patty" aria-label='Reply to Patty'>Reply</a>    </div>
