    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Your words have always inspired me and I&#8217;ve always thought of you as a role model of sorts. I&#8217;m 30 and we&#8217;ve had some overlapping interests and life experiences and this post has just hit home in a big way for me. I&#8217;m nursing my first big real life-changing crush on a woman and I&#8217;ve been with my man for 8 years. I thought I should have had this sexuality part figured out by now? It&#8217;s confusing and thrilling and terrifying all at once. Thank you for speaking your truth. Much love to you and your lovely, growing, changing family.</p>
    </div>

