    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I have so much respect for your incredible writing and ability to share your journey.  I&#8217;m a mom, too. Constantly struggling to teach little ones how to behave even though I haven&#8217;t yet figured out how to be the best version of myself.  Oftentimes I&#8217;m led astray as I weed through the barrage of superficial ideas and images that mainstream media directs at women and mothers. In contrast, your words hit right to the core. They lead me back to what&#8217;s important. Your honesty, authenticity, and bravery are true empowerment tools. We need more voices like yours.  Wishing you all the best.</p>
    </div>

