    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#8217;m not sure I&#8217;ve ever read anything so beautiful and honest and real.<br />
Thank you&#8230;</p>
<p>I started out this post enraptured because I posted something about my father&#8217;s death on my blog, today, and felt really insecure about it. And your parts about it being a bad idea, but something you do anyway resonated with me. </p>
