    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Quickly pulled up your blog to read as I was making dinner. Saddened and then amazed. Thank you for your bravery in writing this. Thank you for your bravery in being honest. And thank you for sharing. I think when we share our struggles with each other, it helps us to all be stronger together. And we can all admit that we all struggle in some way and that no one has it all together. Sending you a lot of love right now!</p>
