      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Jen</cite></div>
      <a href="http://orangette.net/2016/11/november-30/#comment-59968"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2016-12-06T00:22:22-05:00">Tuesday, December 6, 2016 at 12:22 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Oh Molly, I teared up reading this.  I&#8217;ve found that one of the hardest things to accept in life is that personal growth is often acutely painful.  But for those who brave that pain there is a better, happier life on the other side.  The alternative is the slowly corrosive poison of stagnation or living a lie.  I&#8217;m inspired by your bravery.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-59968' data-commentid="59968" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-59968" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Jen" aria-label='Reply to Jen'>Reply</a>    </div>
