      <a href="http://orangette.net/2016/11/november-30/#comment-59969"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2016-12-06T00:25:10-05:00">Tuesday, December 6, 2016 at 12:25 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#8217;m not a person who uses this phrase, but I just kept thinking, &#8220;Bless you&#8221; as I read. Your work has always been honest and brave, and this post is also. xo</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-59969' data-commentid="59969" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-59969" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Amy" aria-label='Reply to Amy'>Reply</a>    </div>
