  <li id="comment-59975" class="comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Vicki Dinsmore</cite></div>
      <a href="http://orangette.net/2016/11/november-30/#comment-59975"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2016-12-06T10:10:17-05:00">Tuesday, December 6, 2016 at 10:10 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I, too, was elated to see a new entry on your site. As I read it, I had to go back several times to determine about whom you were writing. Then it settled in&#8230;you. As always beautifully written. The thing is, you are still Molly, Brandon is still Brandon, and Molly is still Molly, and you have love from everywhere. That&#8217;s what matters. In the end&#8230;we have love. Thank you for sharing. Exhale and enjoy the holidays!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-59975' data-commentid="59975" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-59975" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Vicki Dinsmore" aria-label='Reply to Vicki Dinsmore'>Reply</a>    </div>
  </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-59977" class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1">
