    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I’ve been following your blog for over 5 years and remember crying and getting goosebumps reading A Homemade Life. Your writing always touches me, and this post is no exception. Thank you for being open and courageous and for inspiring others to be honest with themselves as well as others. Thank you for sharing!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-59979' data-commentid="59979" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-59979" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Jane Lee" aria-label='Reply to Jane Lee'>Reply</a>    </div>
