    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Thank you for sharing your courage, your fears, your vulnerability. You inspire so many&#8230;</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-59981' data-commentid="59981" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-59981" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Peggy" aria-label='Reply to Peggy'>Reply</a>    </div>
