      <a href="http://orangette.net/2016/11/november-30/#comment-59993"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2016-12-06T21:01:43-05:00">Tuesday, December 6, 2016 at 9:01 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Your brave, bare honesty are like a light in the darkness. I wish you, Brandon and June the best.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-59993' data-commentid="59993" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-59993" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Jo" aria-label='Reply to Jo'>Reply</a>    </div>
