    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">cptx</cite></div>
      <a href="http://orangette.net/2016/11/november-30/#comment-59999"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2016-12-06T22:21:43-05:00">Tuesday, December 6, 2016 at 10:21 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>My oh my. And I don&#8217;t have the courage to get out of a toxic marriage. Thank you.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-59999' data-commentid="59999" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-59999" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to cptx" aria-label='Reply to cptx'>Reply</a>    </div>
