  <li id="comment-60038" class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Lana</cite></div>
      <a href="http://orangette.net/2016/11/november-30/#comment-60038"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2016-12-08T13:45:31-05:00">Thursday, December 8, 2016 at 1:45 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>So sorry just seeing this.  I am a long time admirer of your prose, sense of humor and sensitivity.  My best friend (we call each other &#8220;our person&#8221; now-thanks Grey&#8217;s Anatomy) came out to me after a 5 year silence from her that until I heard from her, I couldn&#8217;t understand.  That was almost 40 years ago.  So much of what you said is what I have heard her say to me, especially at the beginning of her new life.  Don&#8217;t try to define yourself, just embrace your friends, family and new loves.  It always works out for someone who knows how to live and love.  Sending all my best to you.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-60038' data-commentid="60038" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-60038" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Lana" aria-label='Reply to Lana'>Reply</a>    </div>
