    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Wow! Such overwhelming love and support from all of us readers. I admire you and your honesty and wish you all the best going forward. You can make co-parenting work and you and Brandon will because you know what is important &#8211; LOVE! June has amazing parents. Thanks for sharing your life with me (us). I feel blessed to have stumbled across your blog years ago. Now blessings, love and hugs to you, June and Brandon.</p>
