<p>I haven&#8217;t read your blog in years, my own life having been messy and confused, but I&#8217;m so glad I found this post today (cheers to Autostraddle for sharing). I haven&#8217;t gone through anything like what you have, but with the last year+ of my own wonderful and painful events I feel a little at peace reading this. You&#8217;re going to continue to have a love-filled life.</p>
