    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I am feeling all the feelings for you. I flew out to Seattle to see friends and made them go to Delancey which was epic. I was 30 weeks pregnant with my second, after having PPD and I saw you, June strapped to your chest, writing on the chalkboard, and Brandon, making pizza. I didn&#8217;t say hi because I get shy and don&#8217;t want to be That Creepy Fan. What am I getting at? It was all real. Just like the books, the podcast, the blog. Thank you for always being SO REAL. Rock on.</p>
