    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Molly, this is the first time I&#8217;ve ever written to you, though I&#8217;ve spoken to you in my head while reading this blog or your books.  And thank you &#8211; for your honesty, vulnerability, humility and f**king &#8220;human-ness&#8221; (I needed an adjective to underscore the feeling!) &#8211; what a wonder you are.  This is the reason I keep reading you, checking in with you, loving being included in your life and feelings, and now your sea changes.  Love, love, love &#8211; that is all there is.</p>
