    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I wondered where you went. I missed you, but as someone who is confronting a lot of change in my life, I had the capacity to understand that you would come back when you were ready. Let&#8217;s echo the already beautiful words of you readers: your bravery inspires. And your hair looks great in this picture. Brava to your whole family.</p>
