    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Molly &#8211;</p>
<p>I don&#8217;t know how I missed this post, since I follow you religiously and met you when you came to NYC on your first book tour.  I just want to lend my voice to the chorus of support.  It takes such courage to follow your inner voice and be who you are.  I wish you much love on the journey.</p>
