    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#8217;ve been thinking of this post over the past few weeks since I read it.  I feel your search, your loss and the utter miracle it is to be knocked off your feet sometimes by life.  It is brave to share these things, so I thank you for trusting us to catch you, for allowing us all to recognize how vulnerability brings us closer, makes us stronger.  Much love to you from the East Coast-because love always prevails!</p>
