    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Dear Molly, I haven&#8217;t been reading your blog since the beginning I found it after reading  A Homemade Life. Since then I always come here to check in and see how you&#8217;re doing. I don&#8217;t really know you but in a way I feel like I do really know you. I kept checking in on you this summer and fall, I was worried about you, I don&#8217;t know why I just was. </p>
<p>Everything is going to be fine. You probably already know that, I just wanted to say it anyway because sometimes even though in my heart I know everything will be OK, I need someone to hear my fears and then say the words.</p>
<p>It&#8217;s going to be OK.</p>
    </div>

