    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#8217;ve been following your blog (for years), thoroughly enjoying your books, making your recipes, laughing with your podcasts; and now crying while reading this post. Thank you for sharing such deep and private thoughts with us here. in this space. I admire you in many ways and you continue to inspire me to keep being true to myself.  Sending love!</p>
