    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Molly, your post is so beautifully written and so brave.  I inhaled Delancey and loved your transparency&#8211;that creating a marriage, business, and child can be both magical and hard work.  Your words, profound, painful and alive are an ongoing treasure in my life.  Thank you for your courage.  Please don&#8217;t  ever stop writing.</p>
