    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Oh you lovely and amazing, brave and beautiful woman! Thank you for sharing of yourself so close to the bone. Seeing so many comments here, one thing is clear &#8211; you give voice to what so many of us struggle with &#8211; our identities as women.  Ever so much love and encouragement, And gratitude. Immense and infinite gratitude.</p>
