    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Oh god. I came to Orangette via a link from The Kitchn looking for a red lentil soup recipe, and found this post as well. How beautiful. Reading this aloud to my partner, in tears (the good kind), and thinking of you and your singularly beautiful family as the soup simmers.</p>
