      <a href="http://orangette.net/2016/11/november-30/#comment-60530"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2016-12-28T23:51:28-05:00">Wednesday, December 28, 2016 at 11:51 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Oh Molly.  This is at once both heartbreaking and heartwarming, so vivid and so so raw, yet extraordinarily real.  And for that, we all thank you.  Your honesty is your hallmark.  Having followed your blog, books, insta, etc, since forever, this post is the one that finally made me comment.  You will forge the path through this wilderness with the usual insight and aplomb, have no doubt.  We walk with you.  Thank you for the humanity, and thanks to June and Megan for the sweetest fish.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-60530' data-commentid="60530" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-60530" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Patti" aria-label='Reply to Patti'>Reply</a>    </div>
