    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I have read your blog for a long time and always knew that your words were worth waiting for, whenever they chose to arrive. Your courage holds a light for those who might feel the same struggles. Your path may not be like others but that is because you light your own way with a loveliness that can only be yours. Much love.</p>
