    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#8217;ve been following you for many years now and this post had me spellbound like nothing else.  I felt like you were a close friend telling me all these things and there were so many feels.   You are magnificent and I wish you all the possible smoothness of this journey, and look forward to hearing about where life takes you.   &lt;3</p>
