    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#8217;m not sure how I missed this as I regular reader.  Thanks for your honesty and bravery&#8230; sending love and support from Michigan.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-60598' data-commentid="60598" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-60598" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Chris" aria-label='Reply to Chris'>Reply</a>    </div>
