    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Something happened to my blog reader and your posts haven&#8217;t updated in over a year. I&#8217;ve missed you so much and often wondered, what happened to Molly? How could she just stop writing? Of course in the hurried life of raising two kids I never reached out to ask, but I often wondered about you. I was reading Tara&#8217;s post last night when I found her link to your post. Your writing is so authentic and honest, so real and intimate. I have missed you so much. I&#8217;m so happy to have found you again. Sending love and light on the first day of 2017.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-60630' data-commentid="60630" data-postid="9748" data-belowelement="comment-60630" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Brittney" aria-label='Reply to Brittney'>Reply</a>    </div>
  </li><!-- #comment-## -->
