    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>For someone who&#8217;s obsessed with your blog and check for a new post at least once a day, I completely missed this one. Your fish toys on Instagram brought me here and i&#8217;m completely blown away by your honesty and willingness to share something so incredibly personal with the world. The search of meaning is eternal and any progress, even if it&#8217;s only a millimeter at a time, is still an important step towards self-discovery. Forge ahead, you brave soul!</p>
    </div>

