    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Just catching up after a long break from reading your blog. Woah. I have admired your writing and been a huge fan of the restaurant for years. You are an unstoppable force. I am so proud of you. And what a beautiful example of fully living and growing to show your sweet girl. Kudos Molly. Be happy. ❤</p>
