    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>A fan of yours since the beginning, I have never been more in awe of your ability to to be strong and vulnerable and scared and brave all at once. Thanks for this and for all your writing. It was a pleasure to meet you in September in Cincinnati and I hope our paths cross again.</p>
    </div>

