    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I keep thinking about this post. How people use the term, courage, when you change your life in a way that you weren&#8217;t living before. I keep thinking about how you described this change and yes, it took courage, but also you needed to and were meant to take this way. It&#8217;s a great reminder to me, 34 with a 9 month old baby, that paths and hearts can open to allow more courage, and needtomeantto. I look forward to your posts, and your road ahead. Happy New Year, in the biggest way.</p>
