    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Molly,</p>
<p>Thank you for sharing your brave words and your life with us.  It&#8217;s a gift to read your achingly beautiful writing and feel connected to you and Orangette has had a special place in my life as something delicious, comforting, and real.</p>
<p>I hope you find your happy and comfort in the new shape of your life.  Your words as always inspire me.</p>
<p>With gratitude,</p>
<p>Shila</p>
<p>P.S. I think I speak for many of your adoring readers when I say that we love you always &lt;3</p>
