    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I discovered your blog while in search of a lemon yogurt cake.  I have to say I am so happy to have discovered you!   I read your lovely post with interest.  I am 57 and have three children, aged 30, 28, and 16.  Last year, I married  a woman, much to the surprise of most who know me (there were a few that weren&#8217;t a bit surprised).   Thank you for sharing this story.  It made me feel special and ordinary at the same time, and that is a very good thing.</p>
