    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I have read this post several times now, in awe at your bravery about opening up about something so private and doing it so eloquently. But most of all I am in awe of you being true to yourself. The older I get the less impressed I am by what I thought success looks like &#8211; what I am drawn to instead is people who make the most of this short life, who work towards being true to themselves and others. And it sounds like that is exactly what you are doing and I think that is wonderful.</p>
