    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Dearest Molly. What a circle you&#8217;ve built here &#8211; so many that respect and love you. I am one of those people and am in awe of your bravery and grace. I can imagine the road that got you to this post was rocky but hope the place you are in now is slowly feeling lighter. So much changing. Thank you for sharing and for your vulnerability. It&#8217;s inspiring. Nothing but support and well wishes as you chart these new waters. From a distance, albeit online, I see how you love your people well and I believe that&#8217;s all that matters. xo</p>
