    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I&#8217;ve fallen behind in my blog reading, so just saw this now. First of all, I&#8217;m so sorry to hear about your marriage, but I&#8217;m relieved and happy to know you and Brandon will still be in each other&#8217;s lives, still working together, and still friends. It always seemed like a real-life &#8220;fairy tale&#8221; marriage to me.</p>
<p>I can only imagine how scary it was to go through this huge change and begin telling people about it. I admire your bravery and your decision to go after what makes you happy, what&#8217;s authentic for you. This is never easy.</p>
<p>I&#8217;m sure your openness about it will help many other women. Much love and respect to you, always.</p>
