    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Hi Molly!  I would like to commend your bravery to let it all out in this community. I wish I could also write like you: blunt, honest, real and inspiring. I am one of the readers of orangette who rarely post a comment but I guess this post deserves one. Please extend my regards to Brandon, for also being brave and understanding. I hope you will be both happy, and love June forever and unconditionally. I will pray for your family, I will pray for June, for Brandon and most especially you, I will pray that you may continually inspire us through your writing. Good luck, Molly! We your readers are always here for you.</p>
