    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>It&#8217;s crazy to have so much love for someone I don&#8217;t know and will never meet, but here it is. Viola! This love is for you! Thank you for being the delightful, worthy, whole human that you are and for reminding us all of the complications and beauty and honesty and pain and fullness of a life well lived.</p>
