      <a href="http://orangette.net/2016/11/november-30/#comment-65916"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2017-08-07T14:39:30-04:00">Monday, August 7, 2017 at 2:39 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Years ago I read A Homemade Life and I loved your guys&#8217; love story. I have always loved your blog but I admit I&#8217;m not a regular reader. I hadn&#8217;t visited it in awhile and then in February I found you on Instagram. And I noticed you were no longer with Brandon and instead with Ash. I felt sad. I felt surprised. I wondered. But now I am finally finding this post and wow. Your writing makes me feel like you&#8217;re my best friend confiding in me and I&#8217;m there nodding, listening, ready to be there for you. You are so brave and I admire your life. Keep discovering (and keep writing about it!)</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
