    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Just coming across this now.  I was thinking of you because someone asked about food tours of Seattle.  I&#8217;ve been out of touch with you for so long, but I remember well our visit in NYC, and my quick visit to Seattle with you and Brandon, shortly before your wedding during  a plane layover. All I can tell you is this &#8212; nothing is more perfect, more beautiful, more rewarding than the truth.  You&#8217;ve chosen to live a beautiful and rewarding life, and to be the person who deserves that life and will be at the center of that life.  I wish you all joy, now and every single day.</p>
